{"title":"思海一滴","authors":["纪洞天"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思海一滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"福建明溪县广播站  纪洞天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别了海水，我才知道自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"己的价值。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"影子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请不要根据我的长短来判"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定人的高矮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸵鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凡是有翅膀的都是鸟，管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会飞不会飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叛徒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他生命的天平上，灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是没有重量的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"避雷针"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是为了承担雷电的袭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击，我才乐于高高在上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我平生最讨厌的毛病就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽冷忽热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细菌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的口号是，砸碎显微"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镜。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}